==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tonight
<hw>To*night"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[Prep.
<ets>to</ets> + <ets>night</ets>]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>On this present
or coming night.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>On the last night past.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tonight</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Tonight
<hw>To*night"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The present or the coming night;
the night after the present day.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tonite</ent>⟦br⟧
